{"tid":1524362,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有港豬挂住吃喝玩樂","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T10:14:01.000Z","uid":254281,"like":13,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9353f7f22a28d7a23df8fd7c3429012bc4e762","tid":1524362,"uid":254281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"仲有friend挂住吃喝玩樂，我真係對佢地好絕望。人地為香港付出咁多，佢地就講緊今日食咩，玩咩。香港既未來（佢地既未來）就交比其他人幫佢地爭取，用返工唔太方便講政治野同參加游行做藉口袖手旁觀。<br />\n你地真係唔方便講，唔方便參加， 可以屋企留意下新聞，幫朋友報下消息，做下文宣，做下冷氣軍事都好。<br />\n<br />\n重大日子居然話去玩，事不關己，口裏話唔想送中，心裏自己幫自己送終，等做一世生活在白色恐怖下既港豬。"},{"pid":"217fe49d6d5cc8affbc4d9af95976077017be792","tid":1524362,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70vrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=781c772d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70vrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=111c2281\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70vrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=e61ccf44\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"3667e0cbf1590fdcff84cbe49d6fec5c48b25ecf","tid":1524362,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:16:42.000Z","msg":"手機版喎"},{"pid":"4d20014308d2f56907ed1c3f6e